beer.beer_description:
The legends behind beer cartel have requested we do an XPA for their annual advent calendar. We made a fresh hopped up pale to quench your thirst on a hot summers day.
A combination of tropical fruit lead the charge with this brew. Although light in appearance the flavour packs a great punch of fruity hop perceived sweetness followed by structured bitterness. For the hop heads and novice on a summers

items.badge_description: They know what you want when you walk in the door. That’s right, you don’t have to wait for anyone here.

Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 370 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 75!
